            "element_id": "el_1",
            "element_type": "paragraph",
            "raw_text": "Abstract: This paper presents a comprehensive evaluation of neural machine translation systems across twelve language pairs. We demonstrate that transformer-based models outperform recurrent architectures by 3.2 BLEU points on average across all evaluated benchmarks.",
