            "element_id": "el_6",
            "element_type": "paragraph",
            "raw_text": "Early sequence-to-sequence models (Sutskever et al., 2014) established the baseline for NMT. Attention mechanisms (Bahdanau, 2015) dramatically improved long-sequence translation. The transformer architecture (Vaswani et al., 2017) achieved state-of-the-art results.",
